verbose_text: A non ordered hybrid porous organic-inorganic material, HybPyr, was obtained from a starting mixture of tetramethoxysilane (TMOS) as the silica precursor and an appropriate amount of disilane PyrSil ((R'O) 3 Si-R-Si (OR ') 3), 5, as bridged silsesquioxane (5% mol SiO 2 with respect to total mol of SiO 2), in methanol.
